{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "23", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "08", "M": "41", "S": "55"}}, "news": [{"title": "Allotment of plots in new industrial areas of Indore region to begin from April", "para": "The Madhya Pradesh Industrial Development Corporation will begin allotting plots in nine new industrial areas across the Indore region from April. These developments aim to attract investments in sectors like food processing, confectionery, and plastics, bolstering MSME-driven industries. The expansion includes a large township at Bardari and several smaller clusters to support business growth.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/indore-to-launch-new-industrial-zones-by-april-boosting-msme-growth/129741713?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-1563216/129741713.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Jaipur development body unveils five land pooling schemes", "para": "The Jaipur Development Authority (JDA) has proposed five new land pooling schemes to support urban expansion, including industrial, residential, and mixed-use developments. These plans span areas along Mahal Road, Agra Road, Kalwar Road, and near Tonk Road, covering significant land parcels for diverse development needs.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/jaipur-development-authority-launches-innovative-land-pooling-schemes-for-urban-expansion/129741735?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-189628/129741735.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Supreme Universal to invest \u20b91,500 crore to develop residential project in Pune", "para": "Supreme Universal is set to invest \u20b91,500 crore in a new residential project in Pune's Punawale. The development, named Supreme Rivana, will span 12.6 acres